an mit Lernzielen für die Prüfung</a>\n<span class=\"printonly\">(Link: https://www.dihk.de/resource/blob/67830/a1ba350fb8401daad4f1671ebe8676b8/dihk-rahmenplan-weg-verwalter-data.pdf)</span>\n</li>\n<li >\n<a href=\"https://dserver.bundestag.de/btd/19/226/1922634.pdf\" class=\"extern\" title=\"externer Link\" data-analytics-action=\"Link\" data-analytics-category=\"External\" data-analytics-object=\"https://dserver.bundestag.de/btd/19/226/1922634.pdf\"\nonmousedown=\"if (typeof (ET_Event) !== 'undefined') {_etracker.sendEvent(new et_LinkEvent('https://dserver.bundestag.de/btd/19/226/1922634.pdf', 'External'))}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" >Gesetzesbegründung</a>\n<span class=\"printonly\">(Link: https://dserver.bundestag.de/btd/19/226/1922634.pdf)</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"page-footer footer-picto\" style=\"background-image: url('/blueprint/servlet/resource/blob/6788176/8fe97b1567dbd542043b6292a461fd23/footer-ihk24-data.png')\" data-id=\"page-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"row contact\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p class=\"like-h2\">Wie können wir Ihnen helfen?</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" data-id=\"page-footer-address\">\n<div class=\"like-h6\">Unsere Anschrift:</div>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Industrie-+und+Handelskammer+S%C3%BCdlicher+Oerrhein/@47.993367,7.8374863,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x47911b60ede5f91f:0x7ad94ca95634a245?hl=en\" class=\"address\" title=\"externer Link\" data-analytics-action=\"Link\" data-analytics-category=\"External\" data-analytics-object=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Industrie-+und+Handelskammer+S%C3%BCdlicher+Oerrhein/@47.993367,7.8374863,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x47911b60ede5f91f:0x7ad94ca95634a245?hl=en\"\nonmousedown=\"if (typeof (ET_Event) !== 'undefined') {_etracker.sendEvent(new et_LinkEvent('https://www.google.com/maps/place/Industrie-+und+Handelskammer+S%C3%BCdlicher+Oerrhein/@47.993